---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Desarrollo Web | Pixel 360">
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 bg-primary overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
<div class="space-y-6 reveal in-view">
<h1 class="font-display-hero-mobile md:font-display-hero text-display-hero-mobile md:text-display-hero text-on-primary">
                DESARROLLO WEB
            </h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary/90 max-w-xl">
                Construimos plataformas rápidas, escalables y orientadas a la conversión, integrando diseño a medida y analítica avanzada para tu negocio.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="relative reveal in-view">
<img alt="Desarrollo Web Visual" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-white/20" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCHzzOTKZMrHn0yRGW2E9CnjVnPawSHQrbHl5A5Ma7aq2rN8IuO5D8_LiWoCdxwSeu4tKXGgjVHQk5Sp_X0oG7jHivxfdEnYo1N2TsXQszPPcWDtvjiXMKpfhJovif0IiGetK6wuTsOS3Bf5kGtSybIT-CkX1LxPdlWksHUI9ArXsUJ18b5amiTsxrWeIcDZbkzYcfvf5I3A03cw4BfxdjK7_HqKQnJRudFh-HmQ5M4FFckXTO183VZu1ClgCIWElZoq5hyUYMleGky"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none opacity-20">
<div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface py-16 border-b border-outline-variant/30">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group stagger-fade">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform press-effect">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">responsive_layout</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">Diseño Responsivo</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Experiencias perfectas en móviles, tablets y computadoras de escritorio.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group stagger-fade">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform press-effect">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">bolt</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">Rendimiento Optimizado</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Velocidad de carga ultrarrápida para mejorar el posicionamiento y la experiencia.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group stagger-fade">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform press-effect">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">trending_up</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2">Enfoque en Conversión</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Estrategias de UI/UX diseñadas para transformar visitantes en clientes reales.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4">Nuestros Planes</h2>
<div class="h-1.5 w-24 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex flex-col card-hover stagger-fade">
<h4 class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Express</h4>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-2">Landing Page</h3>
<div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-2xl mb-6">$500 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">- $700 USD</span></div>
<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> 1 página web</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Formulario y botón de WhatsApp</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Hosting, SSL y 1 correo</li>
</ul>
<a href="/producto?service=desarrollo-web&plan=landing-page" class="w-full py-4 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider text-sm press-effect text-center block">CONTRATAR</a>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex flex-col card-hover stagger-fade">
<h4 class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Corporate</h4>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-2">Sitio Web Informativo</h3>
<div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-2xl mb-6">$700 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">- $850 USD</span></div>
<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> 5 páginas (Inicio, Nosotros...)</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Diseño a tu imagen corporativa</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Hosting, SSL y 2 correos</li>
</ul>
<a href="/producto?service=desarrollo-web&plan=web-informativa" class="w-full py-4 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider text-sm press-effect text-center block">CONTRATAR</a>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-xl flex flex-col ring-4 ring-primary scale-105 z-10 card-hover relative stagger-fade">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary text-on-primary px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter">Más Popular</div>
<h4 class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">WhatsApp</h4>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-2">E-commerce a WhatsApp</h3>
<div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-2xl mb-6">$800 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">- $1,000 USD</span></div>
<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Catálogo de productos</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Pedidos directos a WhatsApp</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Hosting, SSL y 2 correos</li>
</ul>
<a href="/producto?service=desarrollo-web&plan=ecommerce-whatsapp" class="w-full py-4 bg-primary text-on-primary font-bold rounded-xl hover:brightness-110 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 btn-magnetic press-effect text-center block"><span class="icon-wrap">CONTRATAR</span></a>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex flex-col card-hover stagger-fade">
<h4 class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Enterprise</h4>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-2">E-commerce con Pasarela</h3>
<div class="text-on-surface font-bold text-2xl mb-6">$1,000 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">- $1,200 USD</span></div>
<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-grow">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Tienda en línea completa</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> 2 pasarelas de pago (tarjeta/PayPal)</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">check_circle</span> Hosting, SSL y 2 correos</li>
</ul>
<a href="/producto?service=desarrollo-web&plan=ecommerce-pasarela" class="w-full py-4 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider text-sm press-effect text-center block">CONTRATAR</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
